rential_Equations_Notes/img39.gif" alt=3D"$\displaystyle =3D h\left( f(y_n,=
t_n) + \alpha h\frac{\partial f}{\partial t} (y_n...
... + \beta k_1 \frac{\partial f}{\partial t} (y_n, t_n)\right)
+ {\mbox{O}}(h^3).$"></td>
<td width=3D"10" align=3D"RIGHT">
(16)</td></tr>
